name: Shaker_Series_Unfinished_Wall_Cabinet_
description:
This handsome cabinet is constructed of pine and maple wood that is unfinished so that you can leave them as-is for a natural look or add your own stain to match your decor. This cabinet features three interior glass shelves. 

 Three fully adjustable glass shelves Shaker style door sits on concealed hinges, door is left undrilled for a knob or handle so you can mount it to open in either directionPerfect as a medicine cabinet, spice cabinet, or storage cabinet  Dimensions: 37.5 inches high x 15.25 inches wide x  8 inches deep Mounts on the wall with built in cleats inside for an easy installationFinish: Natural pine (unfinished)Solid maple door MaterialWoodTypeWall CabinetFinishNatural Finish
